query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('ell',
'mathematica',
'rpg',
'travel')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('bugs',
'combat',
'dnd-3.5e',
'graphics',
'magic-items',
'meaning-in-context',
'numerics',
'passports',
'pathfinder-1e',
'probability-or-statistics',
'sentence-meaning',
'simplifying-expressions',
'transit',
'word-usage')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 100 group by t1.name;
